    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766000/extras/86d17c0aafcbaf1845e7ac2c38f20c59.poster.avif?t=1722853297\" width=620 height=295 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766000/extras/86d17c0aafcbaf1845e7ac2c38f20c59.webm?t=1722853297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在《<strong>Path of Ra</strong>》中，您将陪伴幻化成墓室壁画上象形文字的法老灵魂。您需要移动石板来为法老开路，让他得以收集自己心脏的碎片。通过手工绘制的精美动画，重温法老的故事并发掘他的死亡之谜。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的美术设计</strong></h2>《Path of Ra》以金字塔宏伟的象形文字壁画为灵感，将带领您踏上前所未见的古埃及之旅。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简单好上手</strong></h2>只要滑动手指就能移动及旋转壁画砖，进而重新排列壁画。所有人都能轻松体验本游戏的乐趣。<br>游戏包含超过 60 个精心打造的关卡，当中的每个新壁画都将带来十足的挑战性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766000/extras/d98b1e9d138891823508196a0a02bfca.poster.avif?t=1722853297\" width=620 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766000/extras/d98b1e9d138891823508196a0a02bfca.webm?t=1722853297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766000/extras/d98b1e9d138891823508196a0a02bfca.mp4?t=1722853297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>原创音轨</strong></h2>游戏中采用的音乐和各种声景可让您沉浸在古埃及的温暖氛围中。<br>建议使用耳机以获得最佳体验。",
